title: InfinitiPro by Conair Full Size Salon Performance / AC Motor Dryer
description: The InfinitiPro by Conair Full Size Salon Performance/AC Motor Dryer provides fast, effective drying. With its powerful motor you get up to 50% faster drying time and up to 3x longer life. With its unique Ombre finish, you can do your hair in style. It features 1875 watts, Ionic Technology for less frizz, and 3 heat/2 speed rocker switches for a variety of styles. For additional styling power it features: a true cold shot button, removable filter, hang ring, and concentrator.

title: Infiniti Pro by Conair Limited Edition Blow-Out Hair Dryer
description: The infiniti pro by Conair salon performance ac motor blow-out essentials styling tool gives you up to a 50% faster drying time. Ceramic technology minimizes heat damage and promotes healthy-looking hair, while ionic technology reduces frizz by up to 75%. It has 3 heat and 2 speed switches, with a true cold shot button to lock in style. It also includes blow-out essential tools: round brush, 3 Velcro rollers and 3 sectioning clips.
